title: Sticker Maker Community
description:
Make your own sticker packs as WAStickerApps. You can make Memes, Emoji, animated stickers, or your own photos, any photo from your phone will work.
Discover millions of funny animated stickers and use them in your chats and statuses.
Create your own stickers, even you can make your selfie stickers.
Easily share your best animated stickers to WhatsApp and Telegram through WAStickerApps
